&lt;h2&gt;Details&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The tests were performed on Chrome 79.0, Safari 13.0.4 and Firefox 71.0 (64 bit). The tests &lt;code&gt;RA&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;RB&lt;/code&gt; use recursion. Results&lt;/p&gt;
